#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:40
msgid ""
"\n"
"<format>text='Click a mouse button or press the spacebar to continue...' "
"color=green</format>"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"<format>text=点击鼠标按钮或者按空格键继续…… color=green</format>"

#. [tutorial]: id=tutorial
#. Hello translators! Tutorial is meant to be a bit funny at the start,
#. welcoming new players. Please keep the friendly fun feeling!
#. Any questions email rusty@rustcorp.com.au!"
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:49
msgid "tutorial1"
msgstr "王国教程 第一部分"

#. [objectives]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:155
msgid ""
"You will learn the basics of:\n"
"Movement\n"
"Attacking\n"
"Healing\n"
"Recruiting"
msgstr ""
"你将学习以下基本内容：\n"
" 移动\n"
" 攻击\n"
" 治疗\n"
" 征募"

msgid "Actor"
msgstr "演义圈"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:157
msgid "Destroy a fierce enemy"
msgstr "击败凶残的敌人"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:161
msgid "Get yourself killed"
msgstr "把你自己搞死"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:212
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:218
msgid "Welcome to Kingdom!"
msgstr "欢迎来到王国！"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:214
msgid ""
"For this tutorial, you are playing $scenario_hero.4. Your mentor "
"$scenario_hero.271 is on the east side of the river.\n"
"<format>text='Click a mouse button or press the spacebar to continue...' "
"color=green</format>"
msgstr ""
"在这个教程里，你扮演$scenario_hero.4。你的导师$scenario_hero.271站在河的东"
"岸。\n"
"<format>text=点击鼠标按钮或者按空格键继续…… color=green</format>"

#. [event]
#. [event]: id=student moves 0}
#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:224
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:410
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:532
msgid "Left click on $scenario_hero.name"
msgstr "单击$scenario_hero.name"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:244
msgid ""
"You have selected $scenario_hero.4. The places he can move to are grided."
msgstr "你已经选中了$scenario_hero.4。画有网格的区域是他可以移动的范围。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:256
msgid "Here"
msgstr "这儿"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:262
msgid ""
"Move $scenario.4 next to $scenario.271 by clicking on the tile marked Here"
msgstr "单击标记着“这儿”的六角格，把$scenario.4移动到$scenario.271身边。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:271
msgid "Move $scenario_hero.name to tile labled $here"
msgstr "把$scenario_hero.name移动到标有“$here”的格子"

msgid "Click on $scenario_hero.name"
msgstr "单击$scenario_hero.name"

msgid "Click on tile labeled $here"
msgstr "单击标记着“这儿”的六角格"

msgid "Click on the tile again to end move"
msgstr "再次单击这个格子以结束移动"

msgid ""
"Move troop need tow step, one is move to destination tile, the other is "
"click destination to comform. You have moved to destination, click on the "
"tile again to end move."
msgstr ""
"移动部队操作分两个步骤，一是移动到目的格子，二是单击目标格子确认此次移动。你"
"已经移动到目标格子，接下再次单击这个目标格子以确认此次移动。"

msgid "Move on!"
msgstr "向前冲！"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:296
msgid "Oops!"
msgstr "哎哟！"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:298
msgid ""
"You moved to the wrong place! After this message, you can press right mouse "
"or portrait on panel to undo, then try again."
msgstr ""
"你移动到了错误的地点！读完这条消息后，你可以按鼠标右键或控制面板上单位图像来"
"撤销移动，然后再试一次。"

msgid ""
"You moved to the wrong unit! After this message, you can press right mouse "
"or portrait on panel to undo, then try again."
msgstr ""
"你移动了错误的部队！读完这条消息后，你可以按鼠标右键或控制面板上单位图像来撤"
"销移动，然后再试一次。"

#. [message]: id=student
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:320
msgid "Good morning, $scenario_hero.name! Is it time to attack things?"
msgstr "早上好，$scenario_hero.name！现在是不是该找点东西来揍揍了？"

#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:324
msgid "Um, well..."
msgstr "恩，好吧……"

#. [message]: id=student
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:328
msgid "Have you found an orc for me to fight, huh? A troll?"
msgstr "您找到了兽人来让我练手吗，哈？难道是个巨魔？"

#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:332
msgid "Quiet! I will summon an enemy for you..."
msgstr "安静！我会给你召唤个对手……"

#. [event]: id=student moves 0}
#. [unit_type]: id=Quintain, race=mechanical
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:360
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/units/Quintain.cfg:4
msgid "$scenario_hero.name"
msgstr "$scenario_hero.name！"

#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:364
msgid "... this $scenario_hero.name!"
msgstr "……这是$scenario_hero.name！"

#. [message]: id=student
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:368
msgid "$scenario_hero.name? You want me to fight a dummy?"
msgstr "$scenario_hero.name？您是想让我和一个痞子打斗吗？"

#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:375
msgid ""
"You have $unit.hitpoints hitpoints and a sword, boy. I'm fairly sure you'll "
"win."
msgstr "孩子，你有$unit.hitpoints点生命值和一把剑。我很确定你会赢的。"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:388
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:394
msgid "Attacking"
msgstr "攻击"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:390
msgid ""
"To attack the $scenario_hero.270, first select the attacker "
"($scenario_hero.4) then the target (the $scenario_hero.270). You will see an "
"attack description. When you click OK, $scenario_hero.4 will attack."
msgstr ""
"要攻击$scenario_hero.270，首先要选中进攻方（$scenario_hero.4），然后点击目标"
"（$scenario_hero.270）。你将会看到攻击描述。当你点击“确"
"定”时，$scenario_hero.4就会发动攻击。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:406
msgid "Click on the $scenario_hero.name to attack it"
msgstr "点击$scenario_hero.name以攻击它"

#. [message]: id=student
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:442
msgid "Hey! $scenario_hero.270 fights back!"
msgstr "嘿！$scenario_hero.270会反击！"

#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:446
msgid "Hmm, perhaps we should have started with a doll."
msgstr "唔，也许我们应该从一个玩偶开始。"

#. [message]: id=student
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:450
msgid "Should I retreat?"
msgstr "我应该撤退吧？"

#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:454
msgid "Good idea!"
msgstr "好主意！"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:459
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:463
msgid "Crowns"
msgstr "皇冠"

#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:476
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, you’ve used up your turn attacking $scenario_hero.270. The "
"$scenario_hero.270 now gets to attack."
msgstr ""
"很不幸，为了攻击$scenario_hero.270，你已经把自己的回合用掉了。现在"
"$scenario_hero.270将要发动攻击了。"

#. [message]: id=student
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:487
msgid "The $scenario_hero.270 gets a turn?"
msgstr "轮到$scenario_hero.270了？"

#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:493
msgid ""
"Yes. It's a magical $scenario_hero.270.\n"
"Now, $scenario_hero.270 gets 4 chances to hit you. Brace yourself!"
msgstr ""
"是啊，这是一个魔法$scenario_hero.270。现在这$scenario_hero.270将使用更有利于"
"它的远程战法，有4次机会击中你。打起精神来！"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:496
msgid "Click on the End Turn button in the bottom right of the screen"
msgstr "单击屏幕右下角的“结束回合”按钮"

#. [message]: id=student
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:517
msgid "Ouch! I need to heal! Only $student_hp hitpoints left!"
msgstr "啊！我需要治疗！我只剩$student_hp点生命值了！"

#. [event]
#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:519
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:510
msgid "Village"
msgstr "村庄"

msgid ""
"To avoid attacking, you can move to the other side of the river. Move to the "
"grid that marked village."
msgstr "为避开再次被打，可选择到河对岸去，移动到标有村庄的格子。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:542
msgid "Click on the village to move $scenario_hero.name"
msgstr "单击村庄把$scenario_hero.name移动到那里"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:561
msgid "Villages"
msgstr "村庄"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:563
msgid ""
"You have captured a village! It now flies your flag and has been added to "
"your total village count. (The house icon at the top of the screen shows how "
"many villages you currently control.) Villages provide the gold needed to "
"recruit units. Each turn, you gain two gold plus one for every village you "
"own."
msgstr ""
"你占领了一个村庄！你可以看到它升起了你的旗帜，并且已经被加到了你的村庄总数"
"中。（屏幕顶部的房子图标旁会显示你当前控制着多少个村庄）。村庄会提供金币，金"
"币可以用于征募单位。每回合你将得到两个金币，而你拥有的每个村庄都会产生一个额"
"外的金币。"

#. [event]
#. [then]
#. [else]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:567
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:699
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:732
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:872
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:924
msgid "Click on the End Turn button"
msgstr "点击“结束回合”按钮"

#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:603
msgid ""
"You’re about to be healed by $hp_difference hitpoints, but it’s time to "
"summon some help against that $scenario_hero.270."
msgstr ""
"你就要回复$hp_difference点生命值了，但现在应该召唤一些帮手来对付"
"$scenario_hero.270。"

#. [message]: id=student
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:614
msgid "I’ll recruit some troop!"
msgstr "我会征募一些部队！"

#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:621
msgid ""
"A splendid idea. You can recruit two units if you return to the "
"$scenario_hero.name. You have plenty of gold for that."
msgstr ""
"相当好的主意。如果你回到$scenario_hero.name，就可以征募两个单位。你有很多金币"
"可以用。"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:650
msgid "Recruiting"
msgstr "征募"

msgid ""
"Press Recuit on Panel, Type select $troop1_type, Hero select $troop1_hero1, "
"$troop1_hero2 and $troop1_hero3"
msgstr ""
"按下面板中“征兵”。弹出窗口中兵种选$troop1_type，武将选"
"$troop1_hero1、$troop1_hero2和$troop1_hero3"

msgid "Press Expedite on Panel, move $scenario_hero.name to tile labled $here"
msgstr ""
"按下面板中“出征”，弹出窗口中按下“出征”按钮把$scenario_hero.name移动到标"
"有“$here”的格子"

msgid ""
"No! you recruit wrong. Now distand $unit.name in order to recruit again."
msgstr "不！你征错部队了。现在须要拆散$unit.name部队，以便再次征兵。"

msgid "It isn't time to recruit. Click on the Expedite on Panel to $unit.name."
msgstr "现在不是征兵时候，按下面板中“出征”按钮以拆散$unit.name部队。"

msgid ""
"Press Expedite on Panel, In expedite window, press Disband in $unit.name."
msgstr "按下面板中“出征”。弹出窗口中按下“拆散”按钮以拆散$unit.name部队"

msgid "Um, well...expedite $scenario_hero.name to attack $scenario_hero.270."
msgstr "有部队了，派出$scenario_hero.name去攻击$scenario_hero.270。"

msgid ""
"Now attack $scenario_270! You can hit it on here, he cannot becuase without "
"cast weapon."
msgstr ""
"现在可以攻击$scenario_270！在这儿你可以打到它，它却没有投射战法而打不到你。"

msgid "Let $scenario_hero.name attack to $scenario_hero.270"
msgstr "让$scenario_hero.name攻击$scenario_hero.270"

msgid "In order to defeat $scenario_hero.270, continue to recruit."
msgstr "为彻底击败$scenario_hero.270，征募新部队继续攻击。"

msgid ""
"Press Recuit on Panel, Type select $troop2_type, Hero select $troop2_hero1 "
"and $troop2_hero2"
msgstr ""
"按下面板中“征兵”。弹出窗口中兵种选$troop2_type，武将选$troop2_hero1和"
"$troop2_hero2"

msgid "Attack $scenario_hero.name on here, defeat it."
msgstr "攻击$scenario_hero.name，击溃它。"

msgid ""
"$scenario_hero.4 troop has one hero only, to weak. Let $scenario_hero.10 "
"into it, so need refrom troop, refrom need in city. move hero "
"$scenario_hero.10 and troop $scenario_hero.4 into $scenario_hero.132."
msgstr ""
"$scenario_hero.4部队只有$scenario_hero.4这么个武将，太弱。让$scenario_hero.10"
"加入进来，这就须要重编部队，重编部队只能在城市中，把武将$scenario_hero.10和"
"$scenario_hero.4部队都移进$scenario_hero.132。"

msgid ""
"Press Move on Panel, In move window, move $scenario_hero.10 from "
"$scenario_hero.131 to $scenario_hero.132"
msgstr ""
"按下面板中“移动”。弹出窗口中把$scenario_hero.10从$scenario_hero.131移动到"
"$scenario_hero.132"

msgid ""
"Let $scenario_hero.name be back $scenario_hero.132. move $scenario_hero.name "
"to tile labled $here."
msgstr ""
"让$scenario_hero.name部队回到$scenario_hero.132。把$scenario_hero.name移动到"
"标有“$here”的格子"

msgid "Back city same move, move $scenario_hero.name to $scenario_hero.132"
msgstr "回城操作类似移动，把$scenario_hero.name移动到$scenario_hero.132"

msgid ""
"Press Reform on Panel, In reform window, click $scenario_hero.10, let "
"$scenario_hero.10 into $scenario_hero.4 troop"
msgstr ""
"按下面板中“重编”。弹出窗口中按下武将栏内的$scenario_hero.10头像，让"
"$scenario_hero.10加入$scenario_hero.4队"

msgid ""
"Um, well...don't let $scenario_hero.name go out city, It will be healed by "
"24 hitpoints next turn."
msgstr ""
"嗯，好的……这回合不要让$scenario_hero.name队出城，它的HP太低了。在城里每回合可"
"恢复24HP。"

msgid "Next it is up to yourself to show your talent to deafeat enemy."
msgstr "好的，接下就看你自已了，发挥你的机智，相信你能击败三只敌方部队。"

#. [message]: id=student
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:787
msgid "I’ll tell them to use the one that does the most damage!"
msgstr "我会让他们使用伤害最高的攻击方式！"

#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:791
msgid ""
"And which would that be? The sword (5–4) or the bow (3–3)? I suppose you’ll "
"find out..."
msgstr "那么你认为哪种伤害更高呢？剑（5–4）还是弓（3–3）？我想你会找到答案的……"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:793
msgid "Left click on an Elvish Fighter"
msgstr "左键单击一个精灵战士"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:794
msgid "End your turn and attack again."
msgstr "结束你的回合，然后再次攻击。"

#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:813
msgid ""
"You wouldn’t do anything stupid like charging that quintain yourself again, "
"now would you?\n"
"Use the fighters you recruited first; they’ll be a lot of help."
msgstr ""
"现在你不会去做亲自向着刺靶冲锋这样的傻事了，是吧？\n"
"首先使用你征募的战士们，他们会帮上大忙。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:824
msgid "Left click on the quintain to attack it."
msgstr "左键单击刺靶以攻击它。"

#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:861
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:868
msgid " The ranged attack would have been safer."
msgstr " 远程攻击应该会更安全些的。"

#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:861
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:868
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:880
msgid ""
"Your elf used a sword (5–4; or 5 damage, 4 attacks), which is a <i>melee</i> "
"attack. The quintain defended with its melee attack (3–5)."
msgstr ""
"你的精灵使用了剑（5–4，或者说每次5点伤害，攻击4次），这是一种<i>近战</i>攻"
"击。刺靶会以它的近战攻击（3–5）进行反击。"

#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:869
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:921
msgid ""
"\n"
"End your turn, then attack again."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"结束你的回合，然后再次攻击。"

#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:881
msgid ""
"\n"
"You should tell the other elf to use the bow."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"你应该让另一位精灵用弓。"

#. [else]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:884
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:933
msgid "Attack with the other elf"
msgstr "让另一个精灵攻击"

#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:913
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:920
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:931
msgid ""
"Your elf used a bow, which is a <i>ranged</i> attack (3–3; or 3 damage, 3 "
"attacks). The quintain has no ranged attack, only a melee attack, so it "
"could not defend itself."
msgstr ""
"你的精灵使用了弓，这是一种<i>远程</i>攻击（3–3，或者说每次3点伤害，攻击3"
"次）。刺靶没有远程攻击，只有近战攻击，所以它无法保护自己。"

#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:952
msgid "Keep attacking with both elves until the quintain is finished!"
msgstr "让两个精灵继续攻击,直到刺靶被消灭!"

#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:966
msgid "Maybe you should recruit another elf?"
msgstr "或许你应该再征募一个精灵?"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:970
msgid "Unit Descriptions"
msgstr "单位描述"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:972
msgid ""
"You can right click on a unit to see a detailed <b>Unit Description</b>."
msgstr "你可以右键单击一个单位来查看详细的<b>单位描述</b>。."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:993
msgid "Protect Your Troops"
msgstr "保护你的部队"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:995
msgid ""
"Remember to pull back wounded units into villages and recruit more if "
"needed. Take special care of units with the highest <i>experience points (XP)"
"</i> so they can gain levels and become more powerful."
msgstr ""
"记得把受伤的单位撤回村庄，如果需要的话征募更多的单位。特别要注意保护那些得到"
"最多<i>经验值（XP）</i>的单位，让他们得以升级，并变得更强。"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:1012
msgid "Support"
msgstr "供给"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:1014
msgid ""
"Each village you control will <i>support</i> one unit for free. After that, "
"each unit costs you one gold per turn."
msgstr ""
"你控制的每个村庄都可以免费<i>供给</i>一个单位。超出村庄数目的话，每个单位每回"
"合会耗费你1个金币。"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:1029
msgid "Advancement"
msgstr "前进"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:1031
msgid ""
"When a unit gains enough experience points (the <i>experience bar</i>, if "
"present, is on the <b>right</b> of the <i>hitpoints bar</i>), it will go up "
"a level. Elvish Fighters have two advancement options, and you will be able "
"to choose which one you want. However, second level units cost twice as much "
"to support as first level units."
msgstr ""
"当一个单位获得足够的经验值时（<i>经验值条</i>，如果有的话，会显示在<i>生命值"
"条</i>的<b>右边</b>），它就会升级。精灵战士有两种升级选项，你可以选择你想要的"
"选项。不过，二级单位的维护费用是一级单位的两倍。"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:1046
msgid "Defenses"
msgstr "防御"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:1049
msgid ""
"Whenever one of your units is selected, you’ll see varying percentages as "
"you move the mouse over the map. The higher the percentage, the more "
"<i>defense</i> that unit has in that kind of terrain. For example, most "
"units have good defenses in castles and villages but poor defenses in "
"rivers. However, these quintains use a <i>magical</i> attack, which always "
"has a 70% chance of hitting no matter what terrain its target occupies."
msgstr ""
"一旦选中一个单位，那么当鼠标在地图上移动时，你将看到不断变化的百分数值：数值"
"越高，则该单位在此类地形上的<i>闪避率</i>越高。例如，大多数单位在村庄和城堡中"
"的闪避率挺不错，而在河里则很糟糕。但是，这些刺靶使用的是<i>魔法</i>攻击，所以"
"不管对手占据了哪里，它们都有70%的可能命中。"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:1074
msgid "The rascal is destroyed, and I have gained more experience!"
msgstr "消灭痞子了，而我获得了更多的经验值！"

#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:1080
msgid ""
"Yes, you gain experience through battle, especially by killing an opponent. "
"Gain enough experience and you'll become more powerful.\n"
"Now, I will leave you with more dummies to practice on! After that, we have "
"real work to do..."
msgstr ""
"没错，你通过战斗，尤其是杀死对手来获得经验值。获得足够的经验值之后你就会变得"
"更加强大。\n"
"现在，我会再给你留点假人来练习！结束之后，我们有真正的事情要做……"

#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:1084
msgid ""
"Yes, you gain experience through battle, especially by killing an opponent. "
"Gain enough experience and you’ll become more powerful.\n"
"Now, Li’sar, I will leave you with more dummies to practice on! After that, "
"we have real work to do..."
msgstr ""
"没错，你通过战斗，尤其是杀死对手来获得经验值。获得足够的经验值之后你就会变得"
"更加强大。\n"
"现在，莉莎，我会再给你留点假人来练习！结束之后，我们有真正的事情要做……"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:1121
msgid "Note"
msgstr "提示"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:1123
msgid ""
"These dummies only attack if you are a single tile away. With care, you "
"should be able to kill them one at a time."
msgstr ""
"这些假人只会在你和它们之间只有一格距离时才会进攻。如果足够谨慎，你应该能把它"
"们逐个击破。"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:1132
msgid "Do you want to keep practicing?"
msgstr "你希望继续练习吗？"

#. [option]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:1134
msgid "Yes, I’m still figuring it out."
msgstr "是，我还在摸索呢。"

#. [option]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:1137
msgid "No, I think I’ve got it."
msgstr "不，我想我已经弄明白了。"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:1178
msgid "Victory"
msgstr "胜利"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:1179
msgid ""
"After your victory notice, the map will be grayed out to indicate that the "
"scenario is over, but you will still be able to examine the final positions "
"and state of your troops and any surviving enemies. This is called linger "
"mode. When you're finished, click the End Scenario button to go on the next "
"scenario in the campaign."
msgstr ""
"在你的胜利提示之后，地图会变为灰色，以表示本场景已经结束了。但你将仍然可以仔"
"细查看你的部队以及所有存活的敌人的最终位置和状态。这称为“逗留模式”。当你觉得"
"可以结束时，点击“结束场景”按钮，就可以进入战役中的下一个场景了。"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Speaking.cfg:30
msgid "Undo"
msgstr "撤销"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Speaking.cfg:31
msgid ""
"Don’t forget, you can press <b>u</b> to undo most things; useful for "
"correcting mistakes."
msgstr "别忘了，你可以按<b>u</b>键来撤销大部分操作，这在修正错误时非常有用。"

#. [then]
#. This string used as follows: "<unit name>', your new recruit, has two traits...'"
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Speaking.cfg:78
msgid ""
", your new recruit, has two traits: <i>strong</i> and <i>intelligent</i>. "
"‘Strong’ means a unit does more damage, and ‘intelligent’ means it needs "
"less experience to advance a level."
msgstr ""
"，你的新兵，拥有两项特质：<i>强壮</i>和<i>聪慧</i>。“强壮”说明此单位可以造成"
"更多伤害，而“聪慧”说明它升级所需的经验值较少。"

#. [then]
#. This string used as follows: "<unit name>' has two traits: <i>quick</i> and ...'"
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Speaking.cfg:93
msgid ""
" has two traits: <i>quick</i> and <i>resilient</i>. ‘Quick’ means a unit can "
"move one tile further each turn, and ‘resilient’ means it has more hitpoints."
msgstr ""
"拥有两项特质：<i>迅捷</i>和<i>坚韧</i>。“迅捷”说明这个单位每回合可以多移动一"
"格，而“坚韧”则说明他有更多的生命值。"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:25
msgid "Patch of forest"
msgstr "森林据点"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:26
msgid ""
"Now put an unwounded unit, preferably a Fighter, in that patch of forest on "
"the south-east of the island; a nice, defensible spot."
msgstr ""
"现在，把一个没有受伤的单位，最好是一个战士，移动到岛屿东南部的那片森林里。那"
"是一个良好的防守点。"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:27
msgid "Can one unit survive against all those enemies?"
msgstr "一个单位可以承受那么多敌人的攻击吗？"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:28
msgid ""
"With a little help, yes. If you move your Shaman next to the defending unit, "
"she will heal it 4 hitpoints per turn. Just be careful not to expose the "
"Shaman to attack since she is fairly weak herself."
msgstr ""
"如果给他一些帮助，是可以的。如果你把你的萨满移动到那个防守单位旁边，那她每回"
"合会回复他4点生命值。只要小心一点，不要让萨满暴露在攻击之下，因为她自身相当脆"
"弱。"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:29
msgid "Move a unit (a Fighter if possible) to the patch of forest"
msgstr "移动一个单位（有可能的话最好是个战士）到那片森林中"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:36
msgid ""
"Advance other units onto the island or to capture villages, then <b>End "
"Turn</b>"
msgstr "让其他单位前进到岛屿上，或者去占领其他村庄，然后<b>结束回合</b>。"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:234
msgid ""
"That unit is about one kill (8 experience points) away from gaining a level! "
"Do not let it die!"
msgstr "这个单位再杀死一个敌人（8点经验值）就可以升级了！别让他死掉！"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:287
msgid "I hope I have a chance to retreat after this!"
msgstr "但愿我还能活着回去！"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:298
msgid "One lucky attack by an Orcish Grunt, and I’m done for!"
msgstr "只要一个交好运的兽人步兵再碰到我一下，我就要完了！"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:309
msgid "Ouch! I could make use of some healing in a village."
msgstr "喔唷！我需要去村庄治疗。"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:336
msgid "I have $side.gold gold; enough to recruit!"
msgstr "我现在有$side.gold金币，足够用来征募了！"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:337
msgid "Yes, keep recruiting more units: I think you might need them!"
msgstr "对，不停地征募更多单位。我想你会需要他们的！"

#. [tutorial]: id=2_Tutorial
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:347
msgid "tutorial2"
msgstr "王国教程 第二部分"

#. [side]: type=Orcish Warrior, id=Thrag
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:369
msgid "Thrag"
msgstr "斯拉戈"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:399
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:437
msgid "Capture $scenario_hero.127"
msgstr "占领$scenario_hero.127"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:403
msgid "$scenario_hero.132 fallen"
msgstr "$scenario_hero.132沦陷"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:479
msgid ""
"Ho! Has $scenario_hero.271 conjured something else to beat me with? A flock "
"of scarecrows, perhaps?"
msgstr "呵！$scenario_hero.271有没有召唤些别的什么来揍我？比如说，一群稻草人？"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:481
msgid "This is no game, $scenario_hero.4! "
msgstr "这可不是闹着玩的，$scenario_hero.4！"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:482
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:483
msgid ""
"$scenario_hero.3 have encamped across the river. they are fools to enter "
"here. You must defeat them so they never threaten us again. I will advise "
"you."
msgstr ""
"$scenario_hero.3已经在河对岸扎了营。胆敢入侵这里，他们真是一群蠢货。你必须击"
"败他们，这样他们就再也不会来威胁我们了。我会向你提供建议的。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:485
msgid "What should I do?"
msgstr "我该怎么做？"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:490
msgid "First, you should known troops and heros you can control."
msgstr "首先，你得知道你能控制的部队和武将。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:491
msgid ""
"$scenario_hero.269' s loyalty is less than 112. Loyalty, it is important. "
"Maximal loyalty is 150, if less than 112, he will wander."
msgstr ""
"部队中$scenario_hero.269的忠诚度是103。忠诚度，它是武将一种属性。最大忠诚度是"
"150，一旦小于112，该武将就会下野。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:492
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:493
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:494
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:495
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:496
msgid "Shallow"
msgstr "浅"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:497
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:498
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:499
msgid "Deep water"
msgstr "深水"

msgid ""
"In order to increase loyalty of $scenario_hero.269, need be back city. "
"Unfortunately you cannot, he will wander in next turn."
msgstr ""
"你需要让部队回城以提升$scenario_hero.269的忠诚度，很可惜，部队没有足够行动力"
"回到城中。下回合$scenario_hero.269不得不下野。"

msgid ""
"Since cannot prevent $scenario_hero.269 into wandering, let "
"$scenario_hero.31 capture village."
msgstr ""
"既然已经没法阻止$scenario_hero.269下野，就让$scenario_hero.31去占领村庄吧。"

msgid ""
"There are fresh, finish and wander hero in city. Fresh heros can act in this "
"turn,  finsh cannot act in this turn."
msgstr ""
"城市内有武将和部队，武将分“未”武将，“完”武将和在野武将。“未”武将是本回合还可"
"行动的武将，“完”武将是本回合行动过了的武将。"

msgid ""
"Wander hero doesn't on office, as long as wander hero's loyalty not less "
"than 112, he will recommand in future. But if loyalty less than 130, he "
"maybe move to another city."
msgstr ""
"在野武将是在该城流浪的武将，如果对该城所属君主忠诚度大于112，他在将来哪回合会"
"自荐，从而成为该势力内武将。要注意的是如果忠诚度小于130，他可能会移动到其它城"
"市。"

msgid ""
"In city, loyalty will increase per turn, but it must in troop. if not in "
"troop, as same hero in field troop, he will wander less than 112. Once get a "
"hero less than 112, arm him into troop as soon as possible."
msgstr ""
"城内部队中武将会增加忠诚度。不在部队中的城内武将不会提升忠诚度，而且小于112的"
"话，和城外部队中的一样会下野。所以一旦有了忠诚度小于112武将，尽快让编成部队，"
"让忠诚度至少提高到112。"

msgid "Keep war need gold. Beside villages, there are tow method gain gold."
msgstr "战争需要金币。除去村庄还有两种方法让获得金币。"

msgid ""
"One is fresh hero in city, one fresh hero gain several gold in next turn."
msgstr ""
"一是城市“未”武将，结束回合时该武将还是“未”，那他在下一回合时就会产生数个金"
"币。"

msgid ""
"The other is market, maket can increase city income. Let build a market."
msgstr "二是市场，可以建造市场以提高城市收入。让建造一个市场。"

msgid ""
"Press Build on Panel, Second menu select Market, put market into economic "
"area"
msgstr "按下面板中“建造”，下级中选“市场”，把“市场”放在经济区"

msgid "Build a market complete, income gold per turn is increased."
msgstr "市场造好了，你的每回合金币收入也增加了。"

msgid ""
"In order to get more gold from market, you can set commercial officials in "
"interior."
msgstr "为让市场获得更多收入，你可以在内政中设置主管商业的官员。"

msgid "$scenario_hero.39 is outstanding, defeat it."
msgstr "$scenario_hero.39部队很突出，击溃它。"

msgid ""
"You will find that it is the deep water on bottom right corner of "
"$scenario_hero.39. Defense of troop in deep water is less than land in "
"general.  First, forcing $scenario_hero.39 into deep water."
msgstr ""
"你会发现$scenario_hero.39右下角是深水，部队在水中战力一般比陆地上低，让先把"
"$scenario_hero.39突入深水。"

msgid "Attack $scenario_hero.name with forthcome weapon"
msgstr "用突进战法攻击$scenario_hero.name"

msgid ""
"Do you find the attack of $scenario_hero.31 is reduced by half? That is "
"because $scenario_hero.120 has $scenario_hero.f77 feature in "
"$scenario_hero.39 troop. Normally, he will refuse to submit to you, unless "
"you defeat his army forces. Fortunately, you can use your card to rope in "
"$scenario_hero.120."
msgstr ""
"是不是发现$scenario_hero.31攻击力被减半了，这是因为$scenario_hero.39部队中个"
"持有$scenario_hero.f77特技的$scenario_hero.120。正常情况下要让"
"$scenario_hero.120归顺你，除非把她所属势力灭了，好在你有卡牌。用卡牌拉笼"
"$scenario_hero.120。"

msgid ""
"Click the Card button, and choose the Wander card. Then choose the "
"$scenario_hero.39 on the map. There will be a Pop-up window, and please "
"choose $scenario_hero.120."
msgstr ""
"按下“卡牌”按钮，选择“下野”牌。然后在地图中选中$scenario_hero.39队，出来窗口中"
"选中$scenario_hero.120。"

msgid ""
"Click the Card button, and choose the Office card. Then choose the "
"$scenario_hero.132 on the map. There will be a Pop-up window, and please "
"choose $scenario_hero.120."
msgstr ""
"按下“卡牌”按钮，选择“仕官”牌。然后在地图中选中$scenario_hero.132，出来窗口中"
"选中$scenario_hero.120。"

msgid ""
"The loyalty of $scenario_hero.120 is less than 112, so you should reform to "
"increase his loyalty avoiding wander in next turn."
msgstr ""
"$scenario_hero.120忠度小于112，为不致于下回合就下野，尽快把她编队让提升忠诚"
"度。记得在小于112前不要让出征。"

msgid ""
"Next it is up to yourself to show your talent to occupy $scenario_hero.127. "
"Certainly, I will give you advice in time."
msgstr ""
"好的，接下就看你自已了，发挥你的机智去占领$scenario_hero.127。我会适时向你提"
"供建议的。"

msgid ""
"See this dark blue water? It’s too deep for either side to cross. They must "
"use boat that according to side's navigation civilization."
msgstr ""
"看到那些深蓝色的水域了吗？那些地方水太深，部队要通过它们须借助船只，借助什么"
"船只是根据该势力的航海文明。通过不断水战可以提升势力航海文明。"

#. [else]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:670
msgid ""
"The Shaman is a fairly weak unit, but she has the ability to <i>heal</i> "
"friendly units around her. She also has a special attack which <i>slows</i> "
"enemies, halving the damage they do."
msgstr ""
"萨满是一种相当脆弱的单位，不过有<i>治疗</i>周围单位的能力。同时她也拥有可以让"
"敌人<i>减速</i>的特殊攻击，这种攻击还会让敌人的伤害输出减半。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1099
msgid "Can’t our units just move around him?"
msgstr "我们的单位就不能直接从他身边通过吗？"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1102
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1103
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1104
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1105
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1106
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1107
msgid "ZoC"
msgstr "控制区域"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1110
msgid ""
"No. Once you move close to an enemy unit, you are in its <i>Zone of Control</"
"i> and cannot move further that turn.\n"
"To move your troops onto that island without wading slowly through the "
"water, you’ll have to kill the Grunt."
msgstr ""
"不行。一旦你靠近敌人单位，你就处于它的<i>控制区域</i>内，并且在那回合无法继续"
"深入敌后。\n"
"如果你不想让你的军队缓慢地涉水到达那座岛屿的话，你必须杀掉那个兽人步兵。"

#. [then]
#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1137
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1148
msgid "Advance other units and capture villages, then <b>End Turn</b>"
msgstr "让其他单位推进并占领村庄，然后<i>结束回合</i>"

#. [else]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1140
msgid ""
"No other units can reach that orc. I hope my $unit.language_name survives "
"its counter-attack! I’d better grab more villages and move everyone closer "
"for next turn."
msgstr ""
"其他单位无法接近那个兽人了。但愿我的$unit.language_name能撑过它的反击！看来在"
"下回合我最好占领更多的村庄，让大家再互相靠近一点。"

#. [else]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1141
msgid ""
"Yes. If your Shaman stands just behind that unit on the bridge, she will "
"heal it at the beginning of the next turn."
msgstr "对。如果你的紧靠在桥上单位的背后，那么她会在下回合开始时治疗它。"

#. [else]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1142
msgid "Move your Shaman onto the bridge to stand behind your other unit"
msgstr "把你的萨满移动到桥上，站在另一个单位背后"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1188
msgid ""
"Be careful: if you stand on the bridge you are exposed to attack from "
"multiple directions!"
msgstr "小心：如果你站在桥上，那么你就暴露在多个方向的攻击之下！"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1201
msgid ""
"It’s very dangerous to stand in water when there are enemies about! Your "
"unit will have an 80% chance of being hit! Cancel, and wait for them to "
"attack you!"
msgstr ""
"附近有敌人时站在水里非常危险！你的单位有80%的几率被击中！取消移动，等他们来进"
"攻你！"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1211
msgid ""
"Don’t forget about your Fighter in the east; you can move him south to that "
"last village near the channel."
msgstr "别忘了你在东面的战士，你可以把他向南移动到水道旁边的最后一个村庄里。"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1216
msgid ""
"We need to occupy that village, otherwise they will take it next turn! Move "
"a unit into the village to stop the orcs capturing it. Whichever unit you "
"choose will benefit from the village’s healing, too."
msgstr ""
"我们得占领岛上的村庄，否则下回合他们会占领它的！把一个单位移动到村庄里去，以"
"阻止兽人对它的占领。不论你选择哪个单位，他都会得到村庄的治疗。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1228
msgid ""
"Careful! It is now nighttime. Orcs are <i>chaotic</i>, which means their "
"attacks are now 25% stronger. By day, their attacks are 25% weaker, which is "
"a noticeable difference. You are <i>lawful</i>: stronger by day and weaker "
"at night. Your elvish warriors are <i>neutral</i>: unaffected by the time of "
"day."
msgstr ""
"小心！现在已经是夜间了。兽人是<i>混沌</i>的，这意味着他们的攻击现在会增强"
"25%。在昼间，他们的攻击则减弱25%，这可是很明显的区别。你是<i>守序</i>的：在昼"
"间变得强大，而在夜间变得弱小。精灵则是<i>中立</i>的：不受时段的影响。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1229
msgid "<big>Time of Day</big>"
msgstr "<big>时段</big>"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1231
msgid ""
"\n"
"After this dialog, hold the mouse over the landscape image below the minimap "
"on the right. This brings up a description of the time of day, showing who "
"has the advantage."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"在这对白之后，把鼠标移动到右边小地图上方的风景图上停留一会儿。你将会看到关于"
"时段的描述，以及何类单位在此时具有优势。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1238
msgid ""
"Remember to retreat your wounded units to villages. Healers can only heal 4 "
"hitpoints at a time, while villages can heal 8 (the maximum healing for any "
"unit)."
msgstr ""
"记得让你受伤的单位撤退到村庄里。治疗师们每次只能回复4点生命值，而村庄则可以回"
"复8点（对任何单位来说这都是最大值）。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1245
msgid "Defend here"
msgstr "守卫此处"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1246
msgid ""
"Beware of those orcs crossing the river! If they get into the forest they’ll "
"be hard to dislodge!"
msgstr "注意那些正在渡河的兽人！如果让他们进入森林，那就很难击退了！"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1252
msgid "<big>Tracking Unused Units</big>"
msgstr "<big>跟踪未使用的单位</big>"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1254
msgid ""
"\n"
"You can ensure you use all your troops by pressing <b>n</b> to step from one "
"unit to the next. If you press <b>space</b>, you can mark the currently "
"selected unit as having finished its turn, which stops you moving it by "
"accident later on. When <b>n</b> no longer selects a new unit, it’s safe to "
"end your turn."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"通过按<b>n</b>键依次选中各个单位，你可以确保自己使用了所有的部队。如果按下<b>"
"空格</b>，你就可以将当前选中的单位标记为行动完成，这样就不可能因不小心而移动"
"它了。当<b>n</b>键无法选中新的单位时，就可以放心地结束您的回合了。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1259
msgid "<big>Victory Conditions</big>"
msgstr "<big>胜利条件</big>"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1261
msgid ""
"\n"
"In this scenario, you only need to defeat the orc leader to win. (Victory "
"conditions for a scenario are given under <b>Scenario Objectives</b> in the "
"<b>Main Menu</b>)."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"在此场景中，你只需要打败兽人领袖就能获胜了。（场景的胜利条件在<b>主菜单</b>的"
"<b>场景任务目标</b>中给出。）"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1266
msgid "<big>Recruit the Right Unit Types</big>"
msgstr "<big>征募正确的单位类型</big>"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1268
msgid ""
"\n"
"Remember to recruit troops useful for the situation. Archers are "
"particularly effective against Grunts, Wolf Riders and the orcish leader."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"记得要征募在当前状况下有用的部队。弓箭手们在对付兽人步兵、狼骑兵和兽人领袖时"
"特别有效。"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1286
msgid ""
"Stay near the keep! You need to be on a keep to recruit more units, and I "
"doubt the orc leader will let you use his!"
msgstr ""
"留在城堡主楼附近！你需要站在主楼上才能征募更多的单位，我怀疑兽人领袖是不会让"
"你用他的主楼的！"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1300
msgid ""
"Their leader has moved into that village! He’s not as stupid as I thought. "
"The village heals him each turn and provides good defense."
msgstr ""
"他们的领袖移动到那个村庄里了！他没有我所想的那么愚蠢。村庄每回合都会为他治"
"疗，而且会提供很好的防御（闪避）。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1311
msgid ""
"That unit has captured our village! You’d better get him out; it heals him "
"each turn and provides good defense."
msgstr ""
"那个单位占领了我们的村庄！你最好把他赶出去。村庄每回合都会为他治疗，而且会提"
"供很好的防御（闪避）。"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1323
msgid ""
"Using me to attack is risky! I can slow the opponent with my ranged attack, "
"but I hope you have a plan if I miss!"
msgstr ""
"让我进攻是很冒险的！我可以用远程攻击让对手减速，但是你最好想清楚如果我失手了"
"的话该怎么办！"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1359
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1375
msgid ""
"You are close to killing their leader! The unit who finishes him will gain "
"16 experience points because he is second level. Choose your attacking unit "
"carefully!"
msgstr ""
"你马上就要杀死他们的领袖了！击杀他的单位将获得16点经验值，因为他是一个二级单"
"位。谨慎地选择你的进攻单位！"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1424
msgid ""
"We will miss $deadguy.name| because he had $deadguy.experience experience "
"points. He would have advanced to second level soon."
msgstr ""
"我们会怀念$deadguy.name|的，因为他有$deadguy.experience点经验值，本来他很快就"
"要升到二级了。"

#. [else]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1427
msgid ""
"We will miss $deadguy.name| because she had $deadguy.experience experience "
"points. She would have advanced to second level soon."
msgstr ""
"我们会怀念$deadguy.name|的，因为她有$deadguy.experience点经验值，本来她很快就"
"要升到二级了。"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1444
msgid ""
"We will miss $deadguy.name|, but at least he was not one of our experienced "
"troops!"
msgstr "我们会怀念$deadguy.name|的，不过至少他不是我们的老兵里的一员！"

#. [else]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1447
msgid ""
"We will miss $deadguy.name|, but at least she was not one of our experienced "
"troops!"
msgstr "我们会怀念$deadguy.name|的，不过至少她不是我们的老兵里的一员！"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1462
msgid ""
"Losing a healer hurts all the troops! Keep them out of the enemy’s reach!"
msgstr "失去一位治疗师是对整支军队的打击！保证他们处在敌人的攻击范围之外！"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1463
msgid "<big>Tracking Enemy Movement</big>"
msgstr "<big>跟踪敌人的移动</big>"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1465
msgid ""
"\n"
"You can see where an enemy can reach by moving the mouse over them. You can "
"see all possible enemy moves at once with the <b>Show Enemy Moves</b> "
"command from the <b>Actions</b> menu."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"你可以将鼠标移动到敌人之上以查看他们的移动范围。你可以使用<b>行动</b>菜单中的"
"<b>显示敌方移动范围</b>命令一下子查看到所有敌人的移动范围。"

#. [else]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1469
msgid ""
"Second level units are powerful, but not invulnerable! Goodbye, $deadguy."
"name|."
msgstr "二级单位是很强大，但并非坚不可摧！永别了，$deadguy.name|。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1484
msgid ""
"Beware of the orc leader: he can do 36 hitpoints of damage at night! Attack "
"with many units at once during the day."
msgstr ""
"小心兽人领袖：他在夜间可以造成36点伤害！等到白天，并且同时使用大量单位攻击"
"他。"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1505
msgid ""
"Advancing a level has fully healed me!\n"
"I always have a 60% chance of hitting with my <i>Marksman</i> ability, and I "
"deal 9 damage each for 4 attacks. Use me to dislodge hard-to-hit units."
msgstr ""
"升级让我的生命值完全回复了！\n"
"我的<i>精准</i>技能让我总是有至少60%的几率命中对手，并且我能攻击4次，每次命中"
"能造成9点伤害。让我来对付那些难以命中的家伙。"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1514
msgid ""
"female^Advancing a level has fully healed me!\n"
"I always have a 60% chance of hitting with my <i>Marksman</i> ability, and I "
"deal 9 damage each for 4 attacks. Use me to dislodge hard-to-hit units."
msgstr ""
"升级让我的生命值完全回复了！\n"
"我的<i>精准</i>技能让我总是有至少60%的几率命中对手，并且我能攻击4次，每次命中"
"能造成9点伤害。让我来对付那些难以命中的家伙。"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1530
msgid ""
"Advancing a level has fully healed me!\n"
"I am good with both bow and sword, and I have a special ability: <i>Ambush</"
"i>. I can hide in forests where enemies can only see me if they are right "
"next to me."
msgstr ""
"升级让我的生命值完全回复了！\n"
"我对弓和剑都很擅长，而且我拥有一项特殊技能：<i>伏击</i>。我可以隐藏在森林中，"
"敌人无法看见我，除非他们就在我旁边。"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1544
msgid ""
"Advancing a level has fully healed me!\n"
"I am good with both bow and sword, and I have a special ability: "
"<i>Leadership</i>. First level units around me do 25% more damage, so "
"position me carefully."
msgstr ""
"升级让我的生命值完全回复了！\n"
"我对弓和剑都很擅长，而且我拥有一项特殊技能：<i>领导</i>。我周围的1级单位会多"
"输出25%伤害，所以请谨慎地移动我的位置。"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1559
msgid ""
"Advancing a level has fully healed me!\n"
"I am particularly good with the sword, dealing 8 damage in 4 attacks."
msgstr ""
"升级让我的生命值完全回复了！\n"
"我对剑术特别擅长，拥有4次攻击，每次能造成8点伤害。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1727
msgid "You took too long! We’ll never be rid of these orcs!"
msgstr "你浪费了太多时间了！这样下去我们永远无法击败这些兽人！"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1750
msgid ""
"You have beaten $scenario_hero.3! You may want to try some novice-level "
"campaigns next, such as: Hero Race."
msgstr ""
"你打败了$scenario_hero.3！接着，你可能会想试试看新手级别的战役，比如说“群雄争"
"霸”。"

#. [unit_type]: id=Fighter, race=human
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/units/Fighter.cfg:4
msgid "Fighter"
msgstr "战士"

#. [unit_type]: id=Fighteress, race=human
#. [unit_type]: id=Fighter, race=human
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/units/Fighter.cfg:19
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/units/Fighteress.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Young and brash, Fighters are skilled with swords and are vulnerable to "
"attack from enemies. However, they have the potential to become great "
"warriors one day."
msgstr ""
"战士年轻而又性急，他们懂得一些剑术却很容易受到敌人的伤害。尽管如此，他们仍然"
"有在未来某天成为伟大武士的潜力。"

#. [attack]: type=blade
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/units/Fighter.cfg:24
msgid "sword"
msgstr "剑"

#. [unit_type]: id=Fighteress, race=human
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/units/Fighteress.cfg:4
msgid "female^Fighter"
msgstr "战士"

#. [attack]: type=blade
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/units/Fighteress.cfg:24
msgid "saber"
msgstr "轻剑"

#. [unit_type]: id=Quintain, race=mechanical
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/units/Quintain.cfg:16
msgid ""
"Quintains are used to practice swordplay and jousting on. It would be "
"extremely unusual to be attacked by one."
msgstr "刺靶是用来进行剑术和枪术练习的。被一个刺靶攻击是非常不可思议的事情。"

#. [attack]: type=impact
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/units/Quintain.cfg:24
msgid "flail"
msgstr "连枷"

