#~ msgid ""
#~ "The more likely attack, then, is across the bridge. That middle island is "
#~ "the key: it has a village for healing injured units and forests in which "
#~ "we fight so well."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "接着，他们就最有可能过桥来攻击我们了。中间的小岛是关键：它有一座村庄可以用"
